Recent changes:

Key:
     - Something removed
     + Something added
     * Something changed / fixed

2014-09-29 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Version 0.2.4
    * Works with Debian Wheezy 

2013-11-20 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Uploaded new version of the Password RoundCube plugin.
      File in contrib/roundcube/password/xams.php
      This version is compatible wwith RoundCube 0.9.x and later.

2013-08-30 Arthur Leclerc  arthur@aweb.fr
    * Removed unlimited quota for users.
      Modified user.php and xclass.php. 

2012-12-21 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Fixed a bug in user quota when using unlimited quota in GUI. 
    * Fixed wrong iFrame with Firefox.
    * Fixed missing back return value when deleting in GUI.

2012-11-27 Arthur Leclerc  arthur@aweb.fr
    * Updated version to 0.2.2
    * Fixed typo in xams-apache config 
    * Removed a slash at end in autoreply_files in xams.conf 
      autoreply_files = /etc/xams/autoreply
    * Fixed a bug in GUI during user creation (spamscore not show)
    * Updated various docs

2012-11-23 Arthur Leclerc  arthur@aweb.fr
    * Fixed a bug with spam scores in site creation in GUI
    * Corrected a wrong alignement in Check database consistency in GUI
    * Large cleanup and bug fix in quota engine in GUI
    + New error message and error popup message CSS added in GUI
    * New version of the error.png icon in GUI
    + New critical.png icon for error message in GUI

2012-11-18 Arthur Leclerc  arthur@aweb.fr
    * Updated version to 0.2.1
    * Most of the work of this release in done on the User Interface
    * Modified XAMS header in GUI
    * Corrected a CSS error in DNS interface in GUI
    * Updated regex in Alias forward in GUI
    + Added auto remove of Alias attached to an account in GUI   
    + Added Spam Score Trigger in the Preference, Reseller, site and email account in GUI
    * Corrected some wrong alignement in GUI
    * Modified default values in DNS config in GUI
    * Corrected a bug in errors message for over quota. Messages now using i18.

2012-10-17 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Changed name of XAMS authdaemon init script to xams-authdaemon

2012-10-11 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Various modifications
    + Added debian directory for debian package project in source

2012-09-26 Arthur Leclerc  arthur@aweb.fr
    + Create 0.2.0 SVN branche
    * Changed xams version in various files

2012-09-14 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Various modifications to use XAMS with Debian 6.0

2010-09-12 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Small bug corrected in xmu quota (uninitialized value).
    + XAMS tested with PHP 5.3.3 with success.

2010-09-06 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * New vacation module for RoundCube is ready.
      rc-vacation 0.4 plugin and RoundCube 0.4 needed.
      xams.php removed. All changes are in the README.
    + Added README for RoundCube virtuser_query plugin.
    * Mods in gui/i18n/french/std_menu.xml

2010-08-30 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Various mods for RoundCube 0.4 plugins
      (vacation is still having problems with RoundCube 0.4
      rc-vacation 0.3.2 from bhuisgen@hbis.fr still have bugs too)

2010-08-26 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    + Create 0.1.0 SVN branche
    * Changed xams version in various files
    * Corrected missing database update in updates/0.0.16-0.0.19/mysql/xams.sql
