      in plugins/password/drivers/xams.php

2010-05-26 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Corrected a bug in RoundCube Vacations driver.
      The SQL request was wrong for write in lib/drivers/xams.php

2010-03-08 Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Mods in exim.conf. The line 402 should be deleted
      ( {eq{${lookup SQL_ISALIAS}}{${acl_m1}}}}{1}{0}} )
      Line 401 should be modified.
      It was an insert at the wrong place. This line produce
      an error when VIRUS_MODULE is activated.
    * Various mods in exim4 files.

