2009-11-27  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     + Added Vacation plugin driver for RoundCube 0.3.x
     + Added Password plugin driver for RoundCube 0.3.x
     * Corrected eximfilter.php template

2009-09-15  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Corrected bug in eximfilter.php

2009-09-08  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Added xmu --quota option in xmu.
       This new option replace getmaildirsize and
       sudo script.
       xmu -- quota read maildir size in /var/mail
       and store result in the xams database.
       GUI have been modified according.
       XAMS database has been altered.
       xmu --quota can be play in crontab.

