       is not really useful and have obsolete specs)
       Remove comments in gui/include/xml/menu.xml to
       activate it again.

2008-12-22  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Updated version of SQLSpamSettingsXAMS.pm
       + System to add internal default values for
         Score and HighScore if the database is gone.
       + Default values for LookupScoreList
       + New system to add alias to NoScan (curently
         the system do not manage multiple alias
	 and external alias). TODO
     * Some mods in Exim configuration files.

2008-12-17  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Modified XMU for better handling of EximConfig files
     * Modified XMU to sort tables and SQL queries
     * Modified xams.conf for default EximConfig files
     * New regex to chek local part of email
       "^(([A-Za-z0-9!#$%&'*+/=?^_`{|}~-][A-Za-z0-9!
       #$%&'*+/=?^_`{|}~\.-]{0,63})|(\"[^(\\|\")]{0,62}\"
       To stay crasy for the life!!!
     * More missing i18 found.
     + Added an icon system to display spamcheck,
       spamcheckin and spamcheckout in the site display
       (same system as done for virus).

2008-12-16  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * New version of SQLSpamSettingsXAMS.pm
       Corrected a conflicting bug with the
       Mailscanner SQLBlackWhiteList.pm plugin.
       Added a refresh time system to the plugin.
       The system have a default refresh_time of 15 minutes.
     + Updated XMU to support EximConfig configuration
       files (see http://www.jcdigita.com/eximconfig/)

2008-12-13  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * XML export function is back on the bottom of
       the Overview page. Locale now work and onclick
       now generate an export file with "Save as...".
     + Added --version to xmu
     + Added missing definitions for mailscanner
       in xams.conf
     * Modified printing of used user quota in
       system_overview.php (now show KMG values)
       Sample: Q=334K/1G
     * Modified get_maildirsize routine
     * More documentation file updates
     * Moved new Mysql database schems update to
       updates/0.0.16-0.0.19/mysql/xams.sql

2008-12-11  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Bug solved in user.php in QUOTA selection
     + New i18 system for exim config. Messages
       are now in separated files (exim-message_xx.conf)
     * Various clean-up in exim.conf
     + Added CONFDIR and MAILDIR vars to replace absolute
       paths in most of the Exim code.
     * Modified remote_smtp: transport in exim.conf
     - Removed autogen.conf.debian (only autogen.conf.orig)
     * Modified xmu to handle removing of obsolete site
       in /etc/xams/autoreply.
     * Started to clean-up xams directory, install docs
       and config files.

2008-12-10  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     + Introduced new var in xams.conf -> SETName
       Permit to define MySQL encoding (default UTF8)
     * Modified exim router and transport for autoreply
       to handle UTF8 Subject and Header message with
       complete mime specs.
     + Added MYSQL_SETNAMES var in autogen.conf
     + Added DebugMode in xams.conf
     * Removed dead RBL server in exim-custom.conf

2008-12-07  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     * Mods in reseller.php, site.php, site_template.php
       for SQLSpamScores, SQLHighSpamScores.
     * Mods in startup_checks.php (removed short_open_tag)
     * Mods in i18n/english/site.xml
     * Mods in vspec/users.inc (default value for quota)

2008-12-06  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
     + Added more control on Aliases
     * More i18 on Aliases, Sites and Username

2008-12-05  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    + Added --delete to --delusername to xmu
    + Added control on username when adding a new account
      if the username already exist.
    + Added control on site name when adding a new site
      if the site already exist.
    + name and uniquename are automatically converted
      to lower case when creating new account.
    + site name is automatically converted to upper case
      when creating new site.
    + Added various control on site name, username and uniquename
      when validating forms (specialy bad characters and space)
    * Modified xmu --delusername rm command to handle site
      and username with special characters and space.

2008-12-04  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Modified system_overview.php for better error management
      in the quota module (get_maildirsize).
    + Added --delusername command in XMU maintenance utility
      This new option permit to erase obsolete username
      directory in /var/mail site by site. The system
      check the database et compare with directory in
      /var/mail/.
    * Commented "XHTLM output" in system_overview.xsl
      If you want to use this feature, just uncomment
      the line.

2008-12-03  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Modified French Help files
    * Deleted French text in database structure

2008-11-30  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Modified SQLSpamSettingsXAMS.pm to manage
      Aliases in SQLSpamScores, SQLHighSpamScores
      and SQLNoScan
    + Added database update file in /database/mysql
    * Modified i18 help files (French)
    + Added spamscore et highspamscore for site
      and reseller.

2008-11-29  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Modified SQLSpamSettingsXAMS.pm to use default values
      in pm_preference. These values are used if pm_users
      spamscore and highspamscore are empty.
    * Modified some gui files

2008-11-28  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    + Added SQLSpamSettingsXAMS.pm
      Mailscanner plugin to manage Spam settings directly from XAMS
      Need new database structure
      Setup in preferences.php not yet inplemented. Use vspec for now.
    * Modified files from XAMS gui to manage new Mailscanner features
    * Modified some vspec files to put _IMAP as checked by default

