      Added a test on sender for various addresses
    * Changes in xams_autoreply_transport
      Inactivated copy of original message
      in body of auto reply message (default OFF).

2007-02-10  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Corrected a problem with special characters
      in SQL Macro in exim-sql-macros.conf
    * Corrected a very important bug in exim.conf due to
      a wrong copy/paste. The acl_check_rcpt ACLs
      was not in the right order. Due to this bug,
      SENDER_VERIFY_CALLBACK_DNS
      SENDER_VERIFY_CALLBACK_DYNAMIC
      SENDER_VERIFY_CALLBACK_RBL
      ACLs were not working.
      This bug is present in 0.0.17 release.
    + Added new regex in exim-dynamic_hosts.conf

