2007-02-06  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
    * Removed Exim and XAMS information from SMTP banner
      for security reason.
    * Changes in autogen.conf.orig and autogen.conf.debian
    * Changes in README.Debian
    * Changes in docs/install/debian/sarge/INSTALL
    * Changes in config/exim4/exim-custom.conf
    * Corrected variable in get_maildirsize
