    + Added database/mysql/xams-exim-create.sql
    + Added docs/install/debian/sarge/files/apache-xams
    + Added docs/install/debian/sarge/files/httpd-xams.conf. This
      version of httpd-xams.conf is compatible with Sarge and Etch.
    * New release-catalog
    + Final testing with Debian Etch with or without
      Mailscanner / Spamassassin and SA-Exim.
    + Compatibility list and testing config:
      - Exim 4.63
      - Mailscanner 4.57.6
      - ClamAV 0.88.7
      - MySQL 5.0.32
      - PHP5 5.2.0
      - Courier 0.53.3
      - Apache 1.3.34
      - Firefox 1.5.0.9

2007-02-04  Stephane Leclerc  sleclerc@actionweb.fr
