    * Released version 0.0.13-rc1

2003-05-24  Oliver Siegmar  Oliver.Siegmar@xams.org
    * Merged changes from trunk (0.1 development tree) -
    * Updated MailScanner installation how-to
    * Updated xmu.pl - set 0700 permission when creating mail dirs
    * Changed config/exim4 directory structure
    * removed a perl warning from authdaemon.pl that may have been a bug (if $quota < 0 check)
    * Using macros in exim4 configuration (sourced out SQL statements)
    * Small improvements on exim4 configuration
    * Updated/enhanced Debian/RedHat installation how-to
    * Moved exim transport and router configuration to database
      independent directory
    * Updated PEAR::DB check - version 1.4-final (which we need)
      has been released
    * Removed a few SQL queries from exim4 config files to speed up delivery
    * xams.conf was loaded over and over again by xmu.pl - caused
      insufficient permissions and bad performance sometimes
    * No need to create usernamed dirs in autoreply sitedirs in xmu
    * Declare Exim 3 as obsolet (as Philip Hazel did)
    * Renamed LICENCE in COPYING
    * Renamed ChangeLog in CHANGES

