2002-01-19  Oliver Siegmar  Oliver.Siegmar@xams.org
    * Fixed "Add POP+IMAP user"-Bug - in some cases
      users (POP AND IMAP enabled) couldn't be
      added to a site
    * MaxQuota, MaxAddr, MaxAliases, Quota couldn't
      be CHANGED to unlimited (empty field)
    * Colorized the unlimited-sign ([u]) in system
      overview

