    * Moved the CSS-Files to a seperate directory
      so the access to the include-directory can
      be denied by apache

2002-01-07  Oliver Siegmar  Oliver.Siegmar@xams.org
    * Security enhancements (THERE WERE NO BUGS!)
      It is now possible to specify in config.inc/
      xams.conf if Site- and/or Global-Admins could
      login or not - as it were still possible with users.

