2001-12-22  Oliver Siegmar  Oliver.Siegmar@xams.org
    * Redesigned everything to frames again :-(((
      IE6 Windows, Mozilla 5 Windows, Netscape 4 Windows,
      Mozilla 5 Linux, Konqueror 2.2.1 - _ALL_ have
      shown the site differently. We couldn't fix
      this (height="100%") issue completely :-(
