2001-12-17  Philip Hofstetter  pilif@sen.ch
(actually I made those changes on december the 16th but
 it got midnight when writing this entry :-)
    * Fixed authdaemon that did not take u.AccountState into
      account.
    + Added a sample exim.conf which will be used for all
      further updates in the exim configuration. This
      file can be used out-of-the box for your installation
    + Added support for account-locking in exim

